/02/spiritbox-poppy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/spiritbox-poppy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/spiritbox-poppy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/spiritbox-poppy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/spiritbox-poppy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/spiritbox-poppy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">Spiritbox的</a>女主角考特尼·拉普兰特（Courtney Laplante）在格莱美奖（Grammys）的一次采访中被误认为是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/poppy">罂粟（Poppy），</a>并决定为她的最佳金属表演提名人回答 - 查看下面尴尬采访的镜头。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/poppy-interview-negative-spaces-jordan-fish-3812948">罂粟花升起重心：“坐在极端对我来说很完整”</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（2月2日）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-see-the-full-list-of-winners-3833854">第67届格莱美奖颁奖</a>典礼上走红地毯时，拉普兰特（Laplante）被一家未知出版物接触，接受了一次采访，他将Spiritbox Singer误认为是Poppy。拉普兰特（Laplante）最初给访调员带来了混乱的外观，只是让面试官加倍张望：“你是，你被提名为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/judas-priest">犹大牧师</a>。”</p><p>拉普兰特（Laplante）随后决定在假装是罂粟的同时进行其余的采访：“我是罂粟，我很高兴能在这里被<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/knocked-loose">淘汰</a>。我真的希望我们赢。”</p><p> SpiritBox继续代表真正的罂粟，他过去曾被提名过，“她”很荣幸最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-knocked-loose-and-poppys-epic-jimmy-kimmel-live-performance-3816501">在<em>吉米·金梅尔（Jimmy Kimmel）</em>上踢了敲门</a>。</p><p>拉普兰特（Laplante）补充说：“真的很高兴再次来到这里，很想把格莱美奖带回家，因为我将是第一个赢得这个奖项的女人。实际上，我还没有看过[以前有多少女性]，但我只是知道是我们一个人赢得胜利的时候了。我希望是我，还是Spiritbox和Courtney。”</p><p>查看下面的完整访谈。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="2025年格莱美奖的精神盒采访红地毯" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/r1Wlh-6jLPg?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Poppy尚未公开评论该混音，但在社交媒体上承认它，在她的Grammys帖子的一部分上发布了Instagram上的采访片段，您可以在下面看到。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFl-JB5vvjM/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 