l”</a> 。</p><p>同时，Poppy于去年11月发行了她的专辑“负空间”  - <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/poppy-interview-negative-spaces-jordan-fish-3812948">阅读<em>NME</em>与她聊天有关专辑的聊天</a>。</p><p> Post Spiritbox的Courtney Laplante在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spiritboxs-courtney-laplante-pretends-to-be-poppy-for-grammys-interview-after-awkward-case-of-mistaken-identity-3833962">笨拙的身份案件后，假装在Grammys访谈中被假装为罂粟</a>。</p> ;
