0720" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3760720" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3760720" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/nmixx-viral-staged-getty.jpg" alt="NMIXX病毒分期的音频故障" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/nmixx-viral-staged-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/nmixx-viral-staged-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/nmixx-viral-staged-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/nmixx-viral-staged-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/nmixx-viral-staged-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/nmixx-viral-staged-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3760720" class="wp-caption-text"> NMIXX在2024年。信贷：Chosunilbo JNS/imazins通过Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <strong>2025&#39;NMIXX：Mixx Lab&#39;粉丝音乐会巡回演唱会 - 台北和香港</strong></p><p><strong>2025年4月</strong><br />星期六19至星期日20  - 台北，台湾，NTSU Arena（Linkou Arena）<br />星期六26  - 中国香港，亚洲世界 - 穆斯特</p><p>JYP Entertainment Six Six Piece Nmixx将在亚洲进行几场演出，以参加即将举行的“ Mixx Lab”粉丝音乐会巡回演出。到目前为止，乐队已经在东京，台北，香港和拉丁美洲宣布了演出，将在以后的阶段宣布更多节目。</p><h2>比利</h2><figure id="attachment_3824441" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3824441" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3824441" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billlie-asia-tour-2025.jpg" alt="Billlie Asia Tour 2025" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billlie-asia-tour-2025.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billlie-asia-tour-2025-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billlie-asia-tour-2025-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billlie-asia-tour-2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billlie-asia-tour-2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billlie-asia-tour-2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3824441" class="wp-caption-text">比利。图片来源：Chosunilbo JNS/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <strong>2025年&#39;我们的flowerld：belllie&#39;ve you&#39;世界巡回演唱会 - 香港，台北，大阪和横滨</strong></p><p><strong>2025年2月</strong><br />星期五7  - 中国香港，Heung Yee Kuk NT<br />星期日9  - 台北，台湾，韦斯塔尔<br />星期四27  - 日本大阪，大猫<br />星期五28  - 横滨，日本，横滨湾大厅</p><p>比利（Billlie）于2025年2月在香港，台北，大阪和横滨宣布了他们正在进行的世界巡回演出的“我们的花”巡回演出的亚洲和大洋洲的腿。他们还将在澳大利亚三个城市参观和表演。组织者<a href="https://x.com/studiopav_APAC/status/1877203647051759803">Studio PAV于1月9日宣布</a>，巡回演出的曼谷，吉隆坡和雅加达节目已被取消“由于不可预见的情况”。</p><h2>第6天</h2><figure id="attachment_3782830" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3782830" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3782830" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/day6-world-tour-2024-2025-forever-young-asian-leg-band-aid-album.jpg" alt="Day6 World Tour 2024 2025 Forever Young Asian Leg Band Aid专辑" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/day6-world-tour-2024-2025-forever-young-asian-leg-band-aid-album.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/day6-world-tour-2024-2025-forever-young-asian-leg-band-aid-album-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/day6-world-tour-2024-2025-forever-young-asian-leg-band-aid-album-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/day6-world-tour-2024-2025-forever-young-asian-leg-band-aid-album-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/day6-world-tour-2024-2025-forever-young-asian-leg-band-aid-album-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/day6-world-tour